column5: Beautiful new one bedroom apartment with private keyless entrance. Sub Zero refrigerator, Blue Star Commercial stove, Hansgrohe fixtures with Rain shower head. The bedroom has a queen bed and ample space. Living room includes a full-size mattress pull out sofa couch and flat screen TV with Fiber cable. Located less than a mile to Zilker Park and located right off Lamar Blvd. Easy access to all major roads in Austin. Quiet neighborhood located in the heart of Austin!
column8: Large 1 Bedroom Apt! Super Close to Zilker Park!
